basics.summary:
Callum Dommett is a Middlesbrough based Computer Science student at the University of Teesside, orignally from the surrounding area of Bristol.

Throughout my time as a student I have found a deep passion for developing projects, coupled with my attentive attitude for learning I aspire to bring my thoughts and aspirations for software development to life.

My programming skills consists of Java, Python, C#, and I'm currently looking at incorporating C into this list of languages.
